      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "HARA'S OTIS (2) comes off an average effort last start when eighth at Q Straight over 350m behind Scrub's Blue (19.06) in a OPEN. Was in the money prior to that. Key runner on his best form. GENOVESE (1) was sent out long odds last time but rocketed out of the boxes with a fast early sectional and gave a sight before being swallowed up late, finishing a 6 length second (20.12) over 350m at Grafton. The form out of his last race has been franked. Must be included in calculations. I'M NO MIRAGE (8) improved his time on first attempt this course and distance with a nose win in 25.63 here latest. Harder here but expected to measure up. MANILA PHANTOM (5) placed last time and is worth some thought.",
